web/out/
web/coverage/
web/.turbo/
web/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ESP-IDF firmware outputs and local config
build/
build-*/
**/build/
**/build-*/
**/managed_components/
